    <p><strong>Numra</strong> is a program for practicing numerals. We recommend Numra to all
      students: In order to learn a language you must learn to count in it.</p>

    <p><strong>Options</strong>
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Range: 0–10, 0–20, 0–100 or 0–1000.</li>
      <li>Mode: From number to numeral, and from numeral to number.</li>
